    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
</div>  
</div></div><div class="required-fields group-cta-a field-group-html-element"><h3 class="field field-name-field-cta-one-title field-type-text field-label-hidden field-wrapper" >Accelerate Your Career with a Liautaud MBA</h3><div class="required-fields group-item-one field-group-html-element"><div class="field field-name-field-cta-main-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden field-wrapper"><p>Explore the flexibility and advantages of an MBA from UIC’s Liautaud Graduate School. UIC ranks in the Top 25% of business schools nationwide. Our MBA will set you apart. You’ll earn a proven, research-based MBA and gain hands-on experience and connections to Chicago’s living classroom.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-ds-block-program-important-dates field-type-ds field-label-hidden field-wrapper">  <div class="block block-views block-views-important-dates-block">

